NOTE FOR THE MAINTAINER
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file applies CC BY 4.0 via the official notice above and the canonical
link, which is sufficient to license the work. If you want the *full legal
code* embedded in the repository for offline completeness, paste the verbatim
text from https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode into this file
below this note before public release.

If you instead choose CC BY-NC 4.0 (non-commercial) for the hate-speech corpus,
replace this file with the CC BY-NC 4.0 text/notice
(https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/) and update the license lines
in ../README.md and README.md.
